Actividad carrito de la compra como servicio REST

To launch the REST app the line command is node server.js

Theserver will listen to the port 8000 of the vagrant machine and execute the REST service of the file service.js

In this file (service.js) you can find the instructions to send the right type of request. In fact, for each POST request you have a JASON BODY exemple of how the request should be sent. 

The service we created allows to see the shopping cart, to add or remove an item and to see and modify the almacen MongoDB collection. 

The installation of some supplementary node modules could be necessary.

